{"tid":1605032,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"War is HERE!","createTime":"2019-09-30T07:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T17:18:05.000Z","uid":74778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2be7706a3329aad0300a681a909f85ee1ba8c48a","tid":1605032,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:06:45.000Z","msg":"From TG Group:<br />\n<br />\n#突發 #廣傳 #29sep #30sep<br />\n根據本台實錄<br />\n今晨一批前線手足被人上門拘捕<br />\n而未能確認的個案多不勝數<br />\n部份個案警員已申請搜查令 <br />\n可見已立案調查一段時間<br />\n預計其同僚日內亦將被捕<br />\n<br />\n本次警方偵查行動主要針對自7.1後<br />\n以小隊形式行動的示威者 目標鎖定已久 <br />\n亦有部分被捕者為channel admin<br />\n警員或已從大廈/交通工具cctv<br />\n得知各隊員/隊長行蹤<br />\n<br />\n:warning::warning::warning:請各位提高警覺:warning::warning::warning:<br />\n:pray:🏻:pray:🏻:pray:🏻係時候執一執屋:pray:🏻:pray:🏻:pray:🏻<br />\n<br />\n暫時得知被捕者普遍為參與過<br />\n但亦有人因其他日子被捕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7月1 <br />\n8月25 <br />\n8月31後<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/seqTkDr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FseqTkDr.jpg&h=e3e81357&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c205820e0c603aaf3f527c00dee438efa43c32","tid":1605032,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2369d04746570f908bb0d400a6f3d354b682d156","tid":1605032,"uid":271894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:31:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/